Package com.opengamma.strata.basics.index

Class FloatingRateNames

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.opengamma.strata.basics.index.FloatingRateNames
  • public final class FloatingRateNames
extends java.lang.Object
    Constants and implementations for standard Floating rate names.

    Each constant refers to a standard definition of the specified index.

    If a floating rate has a constant here, then it is fully supported by Strata with example holiday calendar data.
